com.appiancorp.suiteapi.process

Class ProcessDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appiancorp.suiteapi.common.Identity
      • com.appiancorp.suiteapi.process.ProcessProperties
        • com.appiancorp.suiteapi.process.ProcessSummary
          • com.appiancorp.suiteapi.process.ProcessDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LocalId, java.io.Serializable

    public class ProcessDetails
extends ProcessSummary
    Contains detailed information about a process. In addition to the data contained in ProcessSummary, maintains the lists of users and groups that own the task, notes and attachments that belong to the process, and the configuration of the form that is shown to the user that starts the process.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
